. - Develop effective content strategies and establish a sustainable and strategic content approach to marketing. - Co-develop and execute marketing campaigns utilizing Allforcrypto\u2019s brand, mission, and success stories to create clear, engaging and consistent messaging for our two key user groups. - Design and write stories (website, blog) and ad copy (social, email, and display) to support campaign and marketing strategies. What skills do you need? Required: 2+ years of experience creating and managing both written and visual content to distribute across major social media platforms, i.e. Facebook, Twitter Excellent design and copy skills Proficient in managing accounts across all major social media platforms Proficient in using tools like Hootsuite to manage content across multiple platforms Open to sharing your informed and thoughtful feedback Provide regular analytic reporting and strategic analysis Self-starter, motivated, and highly detail-oriented Excited and passionate about your work! Ideal: Experience with social media platforms relevant with cryptocurrency users, e.g. Telegram 3+ years of experience creating and managing both written and visual content to distribute across major social media platforms, i.e. Facebook, Twitter Advanced in managing accounts across all major social media platforms Advanced in using tools like Hootsuite to manage content across multiple platforms Compensation We provide compensation in Allforcrpyto token, AFCT. For this position, the compensation is the equivalent of $2,500 USD per month (for full-time work or pro-rata based on your availability) in AFCT tokens. We will walk you through the process to use the WAVES platform. With your payment in tokens, your work (and compensation) are directly aligned with the growth of Allforcrypto. Let\u2019s start building Allforcrypto together! Skills Social Media Compensation 2500 USD / month Applications for this job are currently closed. ",
